From 3dc13585e9e6320d5c202dd261e6c8a899a583b0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Date: Thu, 28 May 2026 12:00:22 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] deps_guard: whitelist Oniro x86 GPU vendor libs and EGL
 bridges

Add 10 chipsetsdk_dep_whitelist entries:
- libdisplay_buffer_vdi_impl.z.so -> ld-musl loader (passthrough HDI on Oniro)
- 6 vendor GPU libs (libdrm_nouveau/radeon/amdgpu, libelf, libgallium_dri, libvulkan_radeon) -> ld-musl loader
- 3 system libEGL.so -> vendor chipsetsdk libGLESv1_CM/libGLESv2/libEGL bridges. These reflect the Oniro x86 graphics stack layout where opengl_wrapper links against the vendor's Mesa/Vulkan blobs.

Change-Id: I2a1753a21b103dc567cb3a4ce1a1f21c389d59e0
Signed-off-by: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
---
 .../rules/chipsetsdk_dep_whitelist.json       | 70 +++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 70 insertions(+)

